```plantuml
@startuml KuangRD_Autonomous-Driving

package "Autonomous Driving System" {
    [Waypoint Loader] as WP_Loader
    [Waypoint Updater] as WP_Updater
    [DBW Controller] as DBW_Controller
    [Traffic Light Classifier] as TL_Classifier
    [PID Controller] as PID
}

package "External Systems" {
    [Simulator/Car] as Simulator
    [ROS Master] as ROS
}

package "Supporting Libraries" {
    [Eigen] as Eigen
    [uWS] as uWS
    [nlohmann::json] as JSON
    [TensorFlow/Keras] as TF
}

WP_Loader --> WP_Updater : waypoints
WP_Updater --> DBW_Controller : updated waypoints
DBW_Controller --> PID : control commands
PID --> Simulator : steering commands

TL_Classifier --> WP_Updater : traffic light state
WP_Updater --> WP_Loader : waypoint updates

ROS ..> WP_Loader : manages
ROS ..> WP_Updater : manages
ROS ..> DBW_Controller : manages
ROS ..> TL_Classifier : manages

WP_Loader --> JSON : parses
WP_Updater --> JSON : parses
DBW_Controller --> JSON : parses
TL_Classifier --> TF : uses

WP_Loader --> uWS : communicates
WP_Updater --> uWS : communicates
DBW_Controller --> uWS : communicates

PID --> Eigen : matrix ops
WP_Updater --> Eigen : calculations
DBW_Controller --> Eigen : calculations

@enduml
```